<h1>A lexer and parser for Python written in Haskell</h1>

<p>
This package provides a lexer and parser for Python written in Haskell. It supports version 2 and 3 of Python. The parser is implemented using the <a href="http://www.haskell.org/happy/">happy</a> parser generator, and the <a href="http://www.haskell.org/alex/">alex</a> lexer generator. The package also provides a pretty printer, which makes it also suitable for generating Python code. 
</p>

<h2>News</h2>

<ul>
<li> 2009-11-04: Version 0.2 uploaded to HackageDB.
<li> 2009-03-19: Package uploaded to HackageDB for version 0.1.1. 
<li> 2009-03-19: Version 0.1.1 uploaded. 
<li> 2009-03-15: This webpage was created.
</ul>

